para_trans: Regarding the acceptance of the resignation of Inspector Group-A.
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk
Read - Government Order serial number D. 14.01.2026.

Inspector General of Police, Maharashtra State, Mumbai, Shri Santosh Chandrakant Mastud has resigned from the post of Director General of Police, Maharashtra State, Mumbai. It has been approved under the Government Order dated 14.01.2026.
